                    <span>Great baseball (auto)biography.  Fun to read and not just about the game but about life around the game.  There are moments when you cannot help but laugh out loud.  Read this book.  It explains why Boomer is Boomer.
<br />
<br />Recommend: The Last Commissioner - Fay Vincent, Catcher in the Wry - Bob Uecker, Zim - Don Zimmer, anything by Yogi, Moneyball</span>
                  
