                    <span>I was interested in David Wells' life.  This book satisfied that.  To my astonishment, it is incredibly well-written, funny and insightful.  The stories and revellations are great.  Best baseball player's book I've read in years.  Superior on all accounts to the recent David Cone book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">BOOMER BELLOWS</div>
